CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 31, 1946 reads: "Barbour-Jones Nuptials...Wed at St. James Mr. and Mrs. Isaiah Jones Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Wedding party including John Martin, groom Isaiah Jones Jr., bridesmaids Eleanor and Mildred Barbour, bride Betty Barbour Jones, flower girls Patricia and Ada Barbour, and ring bearer Vernard McKenny, posed in front of crushed velvet curtain, another version
